# Vendored third-party source is carried VERBATIM (docs/01-architecture.md A20):
# reformatting it would make every upstream bump an unreviewable diff and would
# obscure exactly what was vendored. `scripts/gate` selects `*.h` as well as
# `*.cpp`/`*.hpp`, so the exclusion has to live where clang-format looks for it —
# a directory-scoped config — rather than in the gate's file selection.
DisableFormat: true
SortIncludes: Never
